    "description": "<p>\r\n\t<u><strong>BUHLMANN SINGAPORE PTE. LTD.</strong></u></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tThe Buhlmann Group is a globally active company. The Group's business activities range from trade in steel tubes, pipes and steel tube fittings to entire pipeline systems. Our range includes an array of materials, from plain carbon steels to high-alloy stainless steels.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tThe Buhlmann Group supplies and advises plant contractors and companies in various sectors, such as the energy, chemical, petrochemical, shipbuilding and mechanical engineering industries all over the world.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tThe Buhlmann Group supplies integrated and complete solutions for the construction of plants, power plants and pipelines. As a global trading company and service provider, the Buhlmann Group stands for competence, quality, a broad product range and also speed, efficiency and punctuality.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t </p>\r\n",
